            <p>The original interface presented a wall of colored icons inside each accordion — dense, flat, and requiring users to click out to another page to see any product detail. Strong background colors dominated entire sections without contributing to hierarchy.</p>
            <p>The redesigned interface uses the same accordion structure but reorganizes what lives inside it. Conditions unfold into clearly labeled sub-accordions. Product lines are identifiable by their spine color before you even open them. Individual products are visible in context. The comparison tool is always a sidebar away.</p>
